title: Amidat musaf le-Rosh ha-Shanah, or Amidah prayer for the additional service of New Year
additional_titles: Handwritten note reading: "קרבן מוס / This Liturgical MS. of the Honan Jews / delivered by them to the Reverend Solomon / Carpenter, at Shanghai, in 1851, was / by him deposited among the Hebrew MSS. / at Mill Yard, 15 Third 1859. Signed: W.H. Black.
